                            <comment id="15882565" author="nkollar" created="Fri, 24 Feb 2017 12:27:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, verified that the patch fixes the failing test&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15884325" author="rohini" created="Sat, 25 Feb 2017 18:16:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1.  This is a better fix than &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-5105&quot; title=&quot;Tez unit tests failing with &amp;quot;Argument list too long&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-5105&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-5105&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and will handle MR and Spark as well. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15893312" author="daijy" created="Thu, 2 Mar 2017 23:59:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually we can remove even more. Jars in the &quot;.ivy2&quot; can also be removed as it is just a repetition of build/ivy/lib/Pig. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15893331" author="rohini" created="Fri, 3 Mar 2017 00:04:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. Only one copy from build/ivy/lib/Pig will be in classpath now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15897407" author="szita" created="Mon, 6 Mar 2017 14:32:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 for &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12855732/12855732_PIG-5156-2.patch&quot; title=&quot;PIG-5156-2.patch attached to PIG-5156&quot;&gt;PIG-5156-2.patch&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
